tagline: Exploring the wiring of your average mouse brain
body:
### Geek + Engineer + Neuroscientist 
Lena spends most of her time doing research in the area of neural computation and machine learning at the Okinawa Institute of Science and Technology. In her spare time she develops iOS games in swift, paints, travels Asia, drinks a lot of coffee and cuddles with her cat called Pankeki.
